additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Active constituent: 50g/kg Iron (Fe) present as Ferrous Sulphate.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Please read all label instructions prior to every use. Do not allow product to spill, or blow over onto hard or non-lawn surfaces. Do not walk over already treated areas, and keep children and pets away from the area until it has been thoroughly watered in. Do not apply on a windy or hot day. Do not apply to dry soil or a moisture stressed lawn. Do not apply to a stressed lawn. Do not apply to acidic soils. Do not exceed rate of application. Do not apply to broadleaf lawns such as dichondra. Do not come into contact with product as staining and irritation may occur.
